/us/texbin is a symlink to any of the modern TeX distributions on  
Mac: gwTeX-2003-2005, gwTeXLive or TeXLive-2007 (a.k.a. MacTeX):

http://www.tug.org/mactex/

or

http://ctan.org/tex-archive/systems/mac/mactex/

